SIGNATURE_NOT_IMPLEMENTED
This file is a placeholder for a detached GPG or minisign signature
over manifest/akashic-envelope.json. Until signature verification is
implemented and tested, Akashic self-integrity is hash-only. Hash-only
self-integrity detects drift but does not prevent an agent with write
access to both files and manifests from rewriting them. Signed or
external authority is required for that guarantee.
